        <p><span class="SetOffFirstLevel">Allow Impersonation </span>This option determines whether the system can post messages to the feed on behalf of the users in response to updates from the external source. Select <span class="Emphasis">True</span> if you want the system to make posts for the users. Select <span class="Emphasis">False</span> if you do not.</p>
